body.name: ZUNMOS Home Office Executive Desk High Back Computer Adjustable Height and Swivel Task Lumbar Head Support Chair, Leather Black
features: Improves Productivity -- The black leather executive office chair with height adjuster adjusts to the height of your desk with a seat height that can be adjusted from 19.5" to 23.4". This rolling desk chair with double upholstered seat cushions allows you to sit comfortably at your desk while working, studying or enjoying your passion for gaming. Maximize your performance at home or in the workplace with a large, wide, comfortable high-back computer chair with wheels.

Built For Comfort -- This home office desk chair is designed to enhance the sitting posture of office workers and help them avoid stiffness, pain and discomfort in the neck and back. This big and tall office chair features an ergonomic S-shaped arch-back design that provides optimal neck and lumbar support. The tilt tension knob underneath the seat adjusts the flexibility of the lumbar support office chair to rock backward, with a tilt angle range of 90° to 110° to help relax back muscles.

Luxury Look Of Leather -- High-quality PU leather headrest, breathable backrest, thick seating cushion, high resilience foam to allow you to sit comfortably for a long time. Soft leather cushion for armrests is durable and easy to clean. It is resistant to corrosion, stains, water, fading and scratches, making it a top choice for upscale conference room office chairs. The elegant, modern and stylish leather office chair is a great gift for office workers, friends, gamers or students.

Sturdy & Durable -- Our modern desk chairs with arms offer a heavy-duty durable nylon base, safety gas lift and rolling casters, they can support adults up to 250 pounds. High back office chairs match with other high-quality office accessories and strictly meets BIFMA Standard to maximally ensure your safety. 360-degree swivel multi-directional wheels ensure smooth-rolling for longer periods of time, providing freedom of movement and the convenience of communicating with others.
Note : To ensure proper assembly, please follow all steps provided in the User manual (provided in pdf below)

Easy To Install -- The tall adjustable office chair comes with all hardware and necessary tools. Most people can follow the assembly video we've uploaded and have it up and running in about 15-20 minutes. This heavy duty office chair is suitable for offices, game rooms, living rooms, bedrooms, dens and more. It will make your space more modern and elegant.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: A Great Executive Office Chair for You! If you are looking for a computer desk chair at home or office, ZUNMOS PU leather office chair may be your best choice. It can hold 250 lbs for max weight, extra padded backrest for more comfort, and chair wheels are super smooth for movement. Meanwhile, the high resilience foam and ergonomic design can support your hours of working with no fatigue. This is a great executive swivel task chair!

Thick & Wide Headrest Thickened & comfortable headrest can better reduce fatigue and protect the cervical vertebra while working or have a rest. Overfilled Lumbar Support Big and thick backrest, padding lumbar, close to the curve of the back, relax your waist and back while working and resting. Padded Armrest Soft armrest pads to provide your arms a comfortable experience. Soft & Flat Seat A double padded thickened comfort seat relaxes the hips, and bears the pressure of sitting for a long time working.

Ergonomic Design The double-layer ergonomic backrest consists of soft elastic cotton and a native sponge that can fit the human spine and support the lumbar. BIFMA Certification Gas Lift High-quality gas lift withstands more pressure and lasts longer Smooth Rolling Casters Quiet rolling, flexible operation, office chair with the 360-degree swivel and smooth-rolling casters

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Recommend - I've had 3
reviews.reviewText: Have worked from home for several years. Will get at least 2 years out of the chair before it begins to feel overly worn. When it does I buy another which speaks for itself. Comfortable, generously sized, good looking, relatively easy to assemble, and durable for 8 hours per day, 5 days a week, for 2+ years.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars A gift for Dad
reviews.reviewText: Bought this chair for my Dad after the one he used for years was looking pretty beat up. A nice chair for the price and was pretty easy to assemble and looks very nice and classy. It's pretty comfortable but doesn't lean back much. My Dad is 350lbs and it holds and supports him with no issues.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Leans you forward, is not s-shaped or ergonomic
reviews.reviewText: Given other reviews, there must be some profoundly serious quality control issues with whoever manufactures this item. First, it's not s-curved (more straight up at the bottom and then arcs slight back after that) and even some of the images suggest it is not (yet other look otherwise - did they also have quality control issues with the renders?), but also it leans too forward when you sit in normal and leaving back doesn't really make that better (unless you pull the bar out and really push back).My dad, however, was fine with it, so I just let him use it and I have ordered a chair that DOES feature an s-curve and a nice bump at the lumbar area. This I can see on that other one in all product images the reviews too.So, it's not that the chair is bad if it comes to you without issue, but far too many people have what is basically a broken product. It might also be the case they are sending out two different chairs - but either way - MOVE ALONG AND BUY SOMETHING ELSE!!!!
